{"tid":246153,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"老母跌咗部電話俾人執咗，嗰個人唔肯俾返部電話佢","createTime":"2017-05-16T19:14:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T20:46:06.000Z","uid":1393,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"42ac4e25aa4cf85845c806f61dc71dfcb8a42828","tid":246153,"uid":1393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T19:14:11.000Z","msg":"佢食完飯落街做運動時跌咗，之後我地打返佢個電話打得通，不過響咗幾聲就俾人cut線。<br />\n<br />\n我估執到個電話個人係廢老，好似連關機都唔識。我地打咗幾次都係響幾聲就俾人cut線。部機仲係小米，完全唔值錢，不過有唔少相，同埋我阿媽冇set密碼，D聯絡人資料完全俾人睇哂。<br />\n<br />\n巴打未瞓可以幫手打呢個電話去叫佢起身痾夜尿。兩點幾打過一次仲打得通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要玩嘅玩埋聽日好啦，因為我阿媽會去報失sim card攞返佢個number .<br />\n<br />\n絕對唔係借刀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/17/031103_1800785c95e228c73b97a622324bd639.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F17%2F031103_1800785c95e228c73b97a622324bd639.jpg&h=aec25701&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/17/031316_623db9d801af2fcdbf293c3f2a2938ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F17%2F031316_623db9d801af2fcdbf293c3f2a2938ce.jpg&h=e18f11ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSMS 係我阿哥send嘅"},{"pid":"8f03b550e944f3f83c1431875e08062c4eab3936","tid":246153,"uid":25673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T19:17:59.000Z","msg":"通左但冇人聽"},{"pid":"c34aca56f8ff38168d2480e3f8b7d252a4c761bd","tid":246153,"uid":115165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T19:18:42.000Z","msg":"暫時未能接通<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9ddb0d0ebc23a226226a9f9134a76dd3524e2a","tid":246153,"uid":1393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T19:19:40.000Z","msg":"可能關咗機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f8e381f88cd013bb29f140126ba7dd16727d70b","tid":246153,"uid":88117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T19:19:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>暫時未能接通<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係"},{"pid":"ae99e9b34c0c796071bb2a54f111840e01f696df","tid":246153,"uid":115165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T19:20:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>暫時未能接通<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係</blockquote><br />\n本身諗住訓唔到同佢傾下計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94e8b0f6f9d1b83f83d431f551314472012962be","tid":246153,"uid":21045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T19:21:04.000Z","msg":"電話唔通嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9069d96315da8404d4d91e05e6b2fe8406b8cace","tid":246153,"uid":57226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T19:22:21.000Z","msg":"同埋我阿媽冇set密碼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad45c8613c8a808d8ed273cd34e965b09cd2f968","tid":246153,"uid":1393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T19:24:42.000Z","msg":"各位有心，如果聽日再打得通我再推post<br />\n<br />\nGood night"},{"pid":"ded8895710f76b42d0af1d06289133b6e6251f63","tid":246153,"uid":17140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T19:25:18.000Z","msg":"不孝子 自爆自己老母電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adfd75ea1a866d6806d670b6776091ec6027e23c","tid":246153,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T19:28:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不孝子 自爆自己老母電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"940db861a42ac1cd5685127ef954428e37fa286b","tid":246153,"uid":20890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T19:28:27.000Z","msg":"